cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

This paper is about building a corpus for direct speech translation, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves speech recognition and alignment, which could fall under cs.SD (Sound). Additionally, the paper involves machine learning and evaluation, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), respectively. Finally, the paper involves multimodal data (audio and text), which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia).
